household_info.name: Florida Family of 4
household_info.description: Two parents (age 40) with two children (ages 10 and 8) in Florida
household_info.key_insight: Florida didn't expand Medicaid, creating a coverage gap for parents between 32% and 100% FPL.

household_info.name: California Couple

household_info.key_insight: This older couple faces high premiums due to age-based rating, making subsidies especially valuable.
